Package com.abstratt.simon.parser.antlr

Class SimonBaseListener

Object
SimonBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
SimonListener, ParseTreeListener
public class SimonBaseListener
extends Object
implements SimonListener
This class provides an empty implementation of SimonListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
